## About Cravo

**Cravo** is a full-stack, production-ready food delivery web application built with the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js) along with Tailwind CSS, Redux Toolkit, and modern cloud services.

**Project Details:**
- **Name:** Cravo - The Online Food Delivery Platform
- **Author:** Harsh 
- **Development Time:** 3 months (Solo Project)
- **Repository:** https://github.com/believeharsh/Cravo
- **Live Demo:** https://cravo.online
- **License:** MIT License

---

## Key Technologies & Services

This project integrates the following technologies and third-party services:

### Core Stack
- **Frontend:** React, Tailwind CSS, Redux Toolkit, Axios, React Router
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, Mongoose
- **Database:** MongoDB (NoSQL)
- **State Management:** Redux Toolkit

### External Services & APIs
- **Cloudinary:** Image and asset management
- **Razorpay:** Payment gateway integration
- **Resend:** Email service for transactional notifications
- **Google Cloud:** OAuth 2.0 authentication
- **Render:** Cloud hosting platform

### Development Tools
- **Husky:** Git hooks for code quality
- **ESLint:** Code linting and formatting
- **Prettier:** Code formatting
- **Git:** Version control

