## How to Attribute Cravo

When using, modifying, or distributing this project, please provide attribution using one of the following formats:

### In README or Documentation
```markdown
Built with [Cravo](https://github.com/believeharsh/Cravo) by [Harsh Dahiya](https://github.com/believeharsh)
```

### In Source Code Comments
```
This project is based on Cravo
Original Author: Harsh Dahiya
Repository: https://github.com/believeharsh/Cravo
License: MIT
```

### In Package.json
```json
{
  "credits": [
    {
      "name": "Cravo",
      "author": "Harsh Dahiya",
      "url": "https://github.com/believeharsh/Cravo",
      "license": "MIT"
    }
  ]
}
```

