## Modifications & Derivative Works

If you modify or create derivative works based on Cravo, you must:

1. Clearly indicate what changes were made
2. Maintain a record of modifications
3. Include the original license in the modified version
4. Provide attribution to the original author
5. Document your changes in a CHANGELOG or similar file

Example modification notice:
```
